#. Tag: title
#: commands.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Tools Menu and Toolbar"
msgstr "Meni Orodja in orodna vrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: commands.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A number of tools are available to aid the design of the symbols. The "
"symbols are composed of a series of sub paths and each sub path is composed "
"of a move to the start position (this defaults to 0,0 for new symbols) "
"followed by lines and curves. The curves are cubic splines having a start, "
"an end and two control points defining the curve. There are convenience "
"tools to create rectangles and ellipses, but these will be broken down into "
"lines and curves."
msgstr ""
"Na voljo so številna orodja za pomoč pri oblikovanju simbolov. Simboli so "
"sestavljeni iz niza podpoti in vsaka podpot je sestavljena iz premika na "
"začetni položaj (to je privzeto 0,0 za nove simbole), ki mu sledijo črte in "
"krivulje. Krivulje so kubični zlepki z začetkom, koncem in dvema kontrolnima "
"točkama, ki določata krivuljo. Obstajajo priročna orodja za ustvarjanje "
"pravokotnikov in elips, vendar bodo ti razdeljeni na črte in krivulje."

#. Tag: para
#: commands.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All points created for the elements are moveable by dragging them to their "
"new position. All points can be snapped to the grid intersections if the "
"snap option is turned on, otherwise they can be positioned anywhere."
msgstr ""
"Vse točke, ustvarjene za elemente, lahko premaknete tako, da jih povlečete "
"na nov položaj. Vse točke lahko pripnete na križišča mrež, če je možnost "
"pripenjanja vklopljena, sicer jih lahko postavite kamor koli."

#. Tag: para
#: commands.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The symbol can be rotated clockwise and counter clockwise and also flipped "
"vertically and horizontally. This allows multiple symbols to be easily "
"created based on the same design. Remember to use the save symbol as new "
"option for this."
msgstr ""
"Simbol je mogoče vrteti v smeri urinega kazalca in nasprotni smeri urinega "
"kazalca ter ga obrniti navpično in vodoravno. To omogoča preprosto "
"ustvarjanje več simbolov na podlagi iste zasnove. Za to ne pozabite "
"uporabiti simbola za shranjevanje kot nove možnosti."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: commands.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here is a screen shot of the tools toolbar"
msgstr "Tukaj je posnetek zaslona orodne vrstice z orodji"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid "Move To"
msgstr "Premakni na"

#. Tag: listitem
#: commands.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<simpara><action>Move the starting position of the sub path</action></"
"simpara> <simpara>If an existing sub path is being created, this will be "
"closed and a new sub path started at the new position</simpara>"
msgstr ""
"<simpara><action>Premakni začetni položaj podpoti</action></simpara> "
"<simpara>Če se ustvarja obstoječa podpot, bo ta zaprta in na novem mestu se "
"bo začela nova podpot</simpara>"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid "Draw To"
msgstr "Riši do"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid "Draw a line to the next selected point"
msgstr "Nariši črto do naslednje izbrane točke"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cubic To"
msgstr "Kubični do"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:172
#, no-c-format
msgid "Draw a bezier curve using two control points and an end point"
msgstr ""
"Nariši Bezierjevo krivuljo z uporabo dveh kontrolnih točk in končne točke"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rectangle"
msgstr "Pravokotnik"

#. Tag: listitem
#: commands.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<simpara><action>Draw a rectangle between two opposite corners</action></"
"simpara> <simpara>This closes any existing sub path and creates a new sub "
"path consisting of the rectangle.</simpara>"
msgstr ""
"<simpara><action>Nariše pravokotnik med dvema nasprotnima vogaloma</action></"
"simpara> <simpara>S tem zapre katero koli obstoječo podpot in ustvarite novo "
"podpot, sestavljeno iz pravokotnika.</simpara>"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ellipse"
msgstr "Elipsa"

#. Tag: listitem
#: commands.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<simpara><action>Draw an ellipse between two opposite corners</action></"
"simpara> <simpara>This closes any existing sub path and creates a new sub "
"path consisting of the ellipse.</simpara>"
msgstr ""
"<simpara><action>Nariše elipso med dvema nasprotnima vogaloma</action></"
"simpara> <simpara>S tem zaprete katero koli obstoječo podpot in ustvarite "
"novo podpot, sestavljeno iz elipse.</simpara>"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert Character"
msgstr "Vstavi znak"

#. Tag: listitem
#: commands.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<simpara><action>Select a character from a font and insert it into the "
"editor</action></simpara> <simpara>This will overwrite any existing paths</"
"simpara> <screenshot> <screeninfo>Here is a screen shot of the character "
"selector</screeninfo> <mediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"charselect-dialog.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </mediaobject> </"
"screenshot> <simpara>The character selector dialog is the standard KDE "
"dialog and allows selection of characters from any font. The size is not "
"used as the character is scaled to fit within the preferred size guide.</"
"simpara> <simpara>Double clicking a character will insert that character "
"into the editor. The dialog will stay open so that another character could "
"be inserted, although this will overwrite the first. This does allow an "
"insert character, save, insert character, save workflow to quickly build up "
"a library of symbols. Ensure that the symbol being edited is a new symbol "
"and not one previously selected from the library, otherwise saving would "
"keep overwriting the one in the library.</simpara>"
msgstr ""
"<simpara><action>Izbere znak iz pisave in ga vstavi v urejevalnik</action></"
"simpara> <simpara>To bo prepisalo vse obstoječe poti</simpara> <screenshot> "
"<screeninfo>Tukaj je posnetek zaslona izbirnika znakov</screeninfo> "
"<mediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"charselect-dialog.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </mediaobject> </screenshot> "
"<simpara>Izbirnik znakov je standardno pogovorno okno KDE in omogoča izbiro "
"znakov iz katere koli pisave. Velikost ni uporabljena, ker je znak "
"prilagojen tako, da se prilega vodniku po želeni velikosti.</simpara> "
"<simpara>Dvojni klik na znak bo ta znak vstavil v urejevalnik. Pogovorno "
"okno bo ostalo odprto, tako da lahko vstavite drug znak, čeprav bo to "
"prepisalo prvega. To omogoča potek dela vstavljanje znaka, shranjevanje, "
"vstavljanje znaka, shranjevanje za hitro sestavljanje knjižnice simbolov. "
"Prepričajte se, da je simbol, ki ga urejate, nov simbol in ne simbol, ki je "
"bil predhodno izbran iz knjižnice, sicer bi shranjevanje še naprej prepisalo "
"tistega v knjižnici.</simpara>"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rotate Left"
msgstr "Zavrti v levo"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rotate the whole symbol counter clockwise 90 degrees"
msgstr "Zavrti celoten simbol v nasprotni smeri urinega kazalca za 90 stopinj"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rotate Right"
msgstr "Zavrti desno"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rotate the whole symbol clockwise 90 degrees"
msgstr "Celoten simbol zavrti za 90 stopinj v smeri urinega kazalca"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "Flip Horizontal"
msgstr "Obrni vodoravno"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid "Flip the symbol across the vertical axis"
msgstr "Obrni simbol čez navpično os"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid "Flip Vertical"
msgstr "Obrni navpično"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid "Flip the symbol across the horizontal axis"
msgstr "Obrni simbol čez vodoravno os"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scale to Preferred Size"
msgstr "Prilagodi na želeno velikost"

#. Tag: listitem
#: commands.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<simpara><action>Scale the symbol to fit within the defined preferred size</"
"action></simpara> <simpara>Note that this only affects the points; where a "
"non filled symbol is created and a line width is defined, this may extend "
"beyond the guide size.</simpara>"
msgstr ""
"<simpara><action>Prilagodi simbol tako, da se prilega določeni želeni "
"velikosti</action></simpara> <simpara>Upoštevajte, da to vpliva samo na "
"točke; kjer je ustvarjen nezapolnjen simbol in je definirana širina črte, "
"lahko ta presega velikost vodila.</simpara>"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable Snap"
msgstr "Omogoči pripenjanje"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:242
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable snapping of points to the grid"
msgstr "Omogoči pripenjanje točk na mrežo"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid "Guide Lines"
msgstr "Vodilne črte"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable the generation of guide lines"
msgstr "Omogoči generiranje vodilnih črt"

#. Tag: title
#: commands.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Settings and Help Menu"
msgstr "Meni Nastavitve in pomoč"

#. Tag: para
#: commands.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
